# General Rules

## Principles
- Simplicity, performance, user experience
- Avoid blocking main thread
- Use ErrorHandler for all user feedback
- Follow existing patterns

## Error Handling
- `ErrorHandler.showError()` for errors
- `ErrorHandler.showSuccess()` for success
- Wrap async in try-catch
- Log with stack traces in debug

## State Management
- Provider pattern
- ChangeNotifiers: RepositoryProvider, ThemeProvider, NavigationService
- Services = business logic (not state)
- Dependencies created in main.dart, passed via constructors
